174
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,450
Mu Chenxi!

175
00:09:37,920 --> 00:09:39,050
Are you all right?

176
00:09:42,680 --> 00:09:43,759
What happened?

177
00:09:43,760 --> 00:09:45,410
Yeah, what's going on?

178
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:47,130
Why did she fall?

179
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,930
No idea.

180
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,690
What's happening?

181
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:56,159
Did someone push her?

182
00:09:56,160 --> 00:09:57,370
I don't know.

183
00:09:57,560 --> 00:09:58,239
What happened?

184
00:09:58,240 --> 00:10:00,170
Did that girl push her?

185
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,039
She just suddenly collapsed.

186
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:02,759
Weird.

187
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:04,050
I'm fine.

188
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:11,490
Did you see that?

189
