191
00:10:38,740 --> 00:10:43,619
♪And on my left shoulder,
your face glows with happiness♪

192
00:10:43,620 --> 00:10:46,019
♪As joy keeps spreading♪

193
00:10:46,020 --> 00:10:48,289
♪With endless affection♪

194
00:10:48,290 --> 00:10:52,140
♪Writing the chapters of us together♪

195
00:10:52,560 --> 00:10:54,849
♪A scorching June♪

196
